'Triumph': not a font; reminds me a lot of [Samantha Italic](http://web.archive.org/web/20141203200347/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/laura-worthington/samantha-upright-script) BTW;  
('MAGIC WIRE': [Brown](http://web.archive.org/web/20141203200347/http:/typophile.com/wiki/lineto.com/The%20Fonts/Font%20Categories/Text%20Fonts/Brown/) LL)  
'L'armature qui se fait oublier': can't find a match but probably custom and exclusive for Triumph; [edit]: got a name and confirming hunch, bespoke typeface called 'Triumph Tailoress Script'; reminds me of [Hubert Jocham](http://web.archive.org/web/20141203200347/http:/www.myfonts.com/foundry/Hubert_Jocham_Type/)'s like [Susa](http://web.archive.org/web/20141203200347/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/hubertjocham/susa) and [Madita](http://web.archive.org/web/20141203200347/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/hubertjocham/madita);
